{
  "id": "adv_main_01_03_01",
  "title": "星見編1章12話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さくら\n君には、このグループを抜けてほしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura.\nI want you out of this group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2666666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "え……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.033333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そして、新たなグループを結成して\nそこでリーダーをやってほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to form a new group‚\nand have you lead that one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.32603193918864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "えええーーーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "EEEEEEEEEHHH?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.62603193918864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 15.159365272521976
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待って\nどういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a minute!\nWhat do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.192698605855306,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "何？\nやっぱり、私がリーダーの方がふさわしいと……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?\nAre you going to argue that I’m the most suited to be the leader?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.2916555205981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "今、そういう話をしてる時じゃないと思うけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ I don’t think now’s the time for that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.758322187264767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "私だけ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.258322187264767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……あ！　いや、突然で驚かせてごめん\nでも、それがみんなを活かす一番の方法だと思うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah! Sorry for springing this on you in sudden.\nBut I really do think this will be the best move for everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.16071864922843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "別々にすることが……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You mean… splitting up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.29405198256176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "このメンバーじゃ、うまくいきそうにないってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you saying the five of us are no good?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.14405193487804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや、違う、それぞれの個性の問題だ\nグループとしての方向性というか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it’s not that. It’s an issue of personalities\nand the direction of the group….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.32292167546496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの、{user}さんが\n一人で決めていいことなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But {user}-san‚\nshould you be the only one making this decision for all of us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.072527349264874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "そうです\nやっと、みんなで進み出そうとしているんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.\nWe’ve finally started to find our footing together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "私は……みんなと一緒がいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I’d rather… stay with everyone else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（しまった。重大なミスを犯したようだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oh no. I think I’ve made a serious mistake.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 70.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 70.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 71.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 71.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃はさくらの側では、自らの輝きに気付けない）\n（さくらは気を遣って本来の自由奔放な輝きを放てない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Kotono is blind to her own light when Sakura is around.）\n（And Sakura can’t display her own free-spirited light out of care for Kotono.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（月と太陽のように遠く離れ、昼と夜）\n（それぞれを司ることで二人は輝くんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（They’re as distant as the moon and sun. Day and night.）\n（Once they embrace who they really are‚ that’s when they’ll both shine.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 89.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（だがそれは客観的に見ているから言えることであって）\n（彼女達からしたら理不尽な要求以外の何物でもない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But I’m only aware of this because I can see them objectively.）\n（As far as they’re concerned‚ I’m just making an unreasonable demand.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 97.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "やーーーーい\n極悪マネージャー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "YAAAAy!\nyou Devil Manager!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 101.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "落ち込んでるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Down in the dumps‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "まあね……でも俺が悪いんだ\n落ち込んでる場合じゃない、なんとかしないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. But I brought it on myself.\nThere’s no time for feeling down. I need to do something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 111.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……そういうとこ、好きだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe… That’s what I like about you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あっ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 115.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 115.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "失敗した時、言い訳とかしないで\nすぐ前に進もうとする所",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whenever you mess up‚ you don’t make excuses.\nYou try to do better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 121.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "私が落ち込んだりしてた時も\nそんな姿勢を見て、なんか気持ちの切り替えが出来た",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whenever I was feeling upset‚\nI’d always get a little boost from watching you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 127.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "なんか、ちょっと照れくさいな\n本当か～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C'mon… You’re making me blush.\nReally?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 132.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
